{"tid":1473442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本向香港發出旅遊警示，香港回歸以來首次","createTime":"2019-08-15T00:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T01:12:38.000Z","uid":278587,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"23ae7c143a81733e0fc766d7ca12167505bbb733","tid":1473442,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1474751_1_20190815061010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1474751_1_20190815061010.jpg&h=bc711a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本外務省因應最新局勢，向香港發出旅遊警示，是1997年香港回歸中國後首次。<br />\n<br />\n外務省發出的警示，屬四級制下最低一級，呼籲日本國民留意香港最新情況，注意安全，並遠離示威及衝突地區。<br />\n<br />\n外務省說，反對修訂逃犯條例引發的相關抗議活動，可能導致局勢變化，包括出現遊擊式抗議，或升級的衝突，而且抗議活動範圍亦擴大到機場與部分觀光景點，估計混亂情勢可能持續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474751-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474751-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=ec12d19c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474751-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=104dac2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474751-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"87396cf2ebf5017d6279df1e697b8e8f5a91a339","tid":1473442,"uid":38381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3ae68a1fb43b5312893418dedd21eb16753436","tid":1473442,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:17:17.000Z","msg":"淪陷⭕"},{"pid":"cbb83f90e97247f21217e475988f705962b430f1","tid":1473442,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458d97e199156aa5064f0be299fca5dda1462e30","tid":1473442,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"攬粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d05b52ed0280e85c018935adbe56eab5219ffa","tid":1473442,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458d97e199156aa5064f0be299fca5dda1462e30","tid":1473442,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"攬粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:33.000Z","msg":"炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f77f30c732853af6e851b3c387a1f1b9e24422","tid":1473442,"uid":12130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=75f41548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=75f41548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"e152f42d98f436e2bf09ae128fb921b13a94a89b","tid":1473442,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563f827d9b7bb9c38b40265e1b7523a473edb432","tid":1473442,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"日本🇯🇵"},{"pid":"8031bfb906b4311c5c400f77a484d4d48d226c16","tid":1473442,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"攪炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafeca4314348d7019ac3bd9f95eb2547c4473b1","tid":1473442,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:39:57.000Z","msg":"人地西方出到第二級<br />\n日本先第一級<img src